Paper: hep-th/9401031

Date: 1994-01-10

Title: Area-preserving structure of 2d-gravity

Authors: D.R. Karakhanyan, R.P. Manvelyan, R.L. Mkrtchyan (Yerevan Physics

Institute)Comments: 8 pages, LaTeX

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B329 (1994) 185-188

The effective action for 2d-gravity with manifest area-preserving invarianceis obtained in the flat and in the general gravitational background. Thecocyclic properties of the last action are proved, and generalizations onhigher dimensions are discussed.